    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija us teem: Juhs effat tee Wirfneeki to Tehwo Nammu starp teem Lewiteem/ fwehtijeetees paschi ar faweem Brahteem/ ka juhs ta KUNga Israēta Deewa Schkirstu augſcham weddat/ fur es tam Weetâ tatatsijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo pirmaē kad juhs klaht ne bijat / darrija tas KUNgs muhsu Deews weenu Plihfu- nun muhsu Starpâ/ tapehz/ ka mehs to ne meklejam / ka tee fa bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fwehtijahs tee Pree- steri un Lewiti/ ka tee ta KUN- GA Israēta Deewa Schkirstu augſcham westu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Lewitu Behrni nef- fe to Deewa Schkirstu/ ittin ka Mohsus bij pawehlejs zaur ta KUNGA Wahrdn / us faweem Kamescheem/ pee tahm Kahrtim/ fo tee us fewim rehmufschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids pawehleja to Lewitu Wirfneeeim/ ka teem bij fawus Brahtus tohs Dsee- datajus peetwest ar spehlejameem Rihkeem / ar Sohma-Stabu- lehm/ ar Kohklehm/ un Pułkste- nischeem/ ka tee staazti dseedatu/ to Balsi pazeldani ar Preeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad eezehe tee Lewiti Eemann Joēta Dehlu/ un no winna Brahteem Affawu Bere- kija Dehlu/ un no Merara Behr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "neem faweem Brahteem/ Enu Kusaja Dehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ar teem fawus Bitus no tahs ohtras Kahrtâ Sakariju/ Benu/ un Jaēsie un Semiramotu/ un Jeēlu/ Unnu/ Elijabu/ un Benaju/ Maēseju/ un Mattiju/ un E weseju/ un Mikneju / un O Eedomu/ un Jeielu tohs Wa tu-Sargus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Dseedataji mans / Affaws un Eetans kahs ar Warra Pułkstenifsche dsirdetees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sakarijus/ un Asi un Semiramots/ un Jeiēls/ Unnu/ un Elijabs/ un Ma jus un Benajus ar finalki sta namahm Sohma-Stabulehm\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Matitius / un E welejus/ un Miknejus/ un Ob Eedomu/ un Jeiēls/ un Asasi ar Kohklehm no astox Stihga preekcha dseedahft.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kenanajus to Lew Wirfneeks bija winnu Usluh tajs/ wiꞥſch pamaztja un w dija tohs/ jo wiꞥſch btja gudre\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Berekijs/ un E nus bija ta Schkirsta Wahrt Sargi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sakanijs/ un Jo wats/ un Netaneēls/ un Ama jus/ un Sakarijus/ un Benaju un Eliēsers tee Preesteri/puhte Trummnetehm preeksch to Da wa Schkirstu/ un Obed-Eedom un Jekijus bija ta Schkir Wahrtu-Sargi.\n"
    }
